[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering how to handle channel counts. For multiple channels, I think the count should increment per channel, but for a single channel, it’s just one command count. When re-subscribing to the same channel, Redis counts it as one, not two.
[thinking] 
[thinking] Using a separate AtomicInteger for commands and tracking response subscription counts could work. I should probably write the count as command.size and adjust it for awaiting subscriptions. Editing to use the active count seems smart. Psubscribe may not need to worry about this.
